e: ￹`Ma~`senger~ `ko~ `riko'~ `ako~.￺My clothes are damp / wet.￻我的衣服被淋濕
￹`Ma~`senger~ `no~ `'orad~ `ko~ `sera~.￺The rain wet the ground.￻雨水滋潤大地
￹`Sngeren~ `ko~ `felac~.￺Wash the rice for cooking.￻淘米煮飯，把米浸在水中

d.f: ￹￺a species of tree * Formosan Sweet Gum * Fragrant Maple (Liquidambar formosana Hance)￻一種樹，有香味的槭 (楓香)
